^StateMachine|description:Intent Core conditional state routing _|

#comment|Initialize current state and previous memory _|
#current_state|idle _|
#previous_state|@#current_state _|

!|log:Current state is:#current_state; Previous was:#previous_state _|

!?|#current_state:idle
    !|log:System is resting _|
_|
?!|#current_state:loading
    !|log:System is loading _|
_|
?!|#current_state:active
    !|log:System is active _|
_|
?!|#current_state:error
    !|warn:An error has occurred _|
_|
?!|#current_state:shutdown
    !|log:System is shutting down _|
_|
?!|
    !|warn:State #current_state is undefined _|
_|

#last_idle|@#current_state _|
